2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person who likes grey is the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who likes grey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Color   | lilac | azure   | grey   |
| Sport           | rugby   | parkour | sailing     |
| Transport     | bike   | van    | jet-ski |

