.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, dutch, pakistani
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, horror, sports
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the french##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person watching horror movies and the person drinking iced-tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |
| Nationality         | dutch   | french | pakistani |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | sports      | horror  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | hot-chocolate   | sprite |

