2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the fan of folk is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's sport is baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | folk    | pop |
| Sport         | baseball   | tennis     | sailing     |
| Birthday     | july | june | october     |

