.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-8::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, cucumber, garlic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, indie, r&b
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, pakistani
1. the person eating garlic is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the person eating watermelon is between the fan of indie and the american##2
4. the fan of indie is the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food         | garlic | watermelon | cucumber  |
| Music-Genre   | indie        | r&b        | electronic |
| Nationality         | argentine         | pakistani    | american   |

