.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, coffee
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog, pony
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, argentine, mexican
1. the person drinking lemonade is between the owner of the pony and the person drinking milk##2
2. the mexican is between the indian and the person drinking milk##2
3. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage         | coffee | lemonade  | milk  |
| Pet         | pony    | chinchilla | hedgehog |
| Nationality   | indian    | mexican       | argentine  |

