.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, jazz, r&b
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony, brown
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, vegafina, ritmeester
1. the person who likes mauve is the havana-smoker##1
2. the fan of indie is between the person who likes ebony and the fan of r&b##2
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | indie         | r&b      |
| Color   | ebony | brown       | mauve |
| Cigar         | ritmeester     | vegafina | havana |

