.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, begonia-climbing, august
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, begonia
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, skiing
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |       3       |
| Birthday         | august | september  | begonia-climbing |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | daffodil       | begonia          |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | skateboarding | skiing        |

