The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, sports, time-travel
There 3 different types of food: apple, raspberry, plum
1. the person eating apple is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person eating plum##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3       |
| Transport           | skateboard   | helicopter | train |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | drama     | sports       |
| Food   | raspberry    | apple | plum       |

