.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking, chess
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, russian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, january, may
1. the russian is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Hobby          | filmmaking      | sudoku | chess     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | russian  | argentine     |
| Birthday         | may  | march | january |

