The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, july, november
There 3 different types of food: apple, raspberry, pumpkin
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person eating raspberry is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person watching epic movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |      2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | documentary | disaster   |
| Birthday           | september  | july        | november     |
| Food     | apple  | raspberry   | pumpkin |

