.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, adventure
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, police-officer, librarian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, funk, punk
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the designer##1
2. the fan of funk is between the librarian and the person watching crime movies##2
3. the police-officer is between the fan of blues and the person watching disaster movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |    3    |
| Movie-Genre      | disaster    | adventure  | crime |
| Job          | librarian | police-officer | designer |
| Music-Genre   | punk      | funk | blues   |

