.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, green, ivory
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, car, motorbike
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who likes fuchsia##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea | juice     |
| Color           | ivory      | green | fuchsia     |
| Transport   | car       | motorbike      | roller |

