.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, orange, chestnut
3 different games are played: snooker, billiard, mah-jongg
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person playing billiard##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby         | card-games | singing | skydiving |
| Color           | orange   | chestnut   | brown |
| Game   | mah-jongg     | snooker | billiard   |

