.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, cricket
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, singing, woodworking
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, brazilian
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the brazilian##2
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the indonesian##1
3. the australian is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |      3       |
| Sport   | cricket | snowboarding      | sailing  |
| Hobby      | woodworking   | singing   | reading      |
| Nationality        | indonesian     | australian | brazilian |

