.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, december, october
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, singing, skydiving
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, handball, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Birthday    | october     | may     | december |
| Hobby       | skydiving | filmmaking | singing |
| Sport   | baseball     | surfing       | handball    |

 